casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Papp v. Norton, Judge.

[Cite as State ex rel. Papp v. Norton (1993), 66 Ohio St.3d 1221.]

(No. 93-126 Submitted May 18, 1993 Decided June 30, 1993.) Kay L. Williams, for relator. Richards & Meóla, Charles L. Richards and Jeffrey V. Goodman, for respondent.

*1222The motion for rehearing of the decision rendered in 66 Ohio St.3d 162, 610 N.E.2d 979, is denied. The court notes that documents filed by respondent, Judge Thomas F. Norton, demonstrate that respondent has properly complied with this court’s preemptory writ.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Resnick, J., not participating.
